OL,3,CGlasgow University accused of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' in report into
OL,5,Cstudent's death
OL,7,FA Quality Assurance Agency review has
OL,8,Fhighlighted serious systemic risks in
OL,9,Facademic processes at the University
OL,10,Fof Glasgow after a student took his
OL,11,Fown life following a grading error, a
OL,12,Freport has found.
OL,14,FEthan Brown took his own life on
OL,15,FDecember 13, 2024, the day he should
OL,16,Fhave been graduating, and was found
OL,17,Fdead in his bedroom by his mother,
OL,18,FTracy Scott, early that morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
