OL,3,CGlasgow University accused of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' in report into
OL,5,Cstudent's death
OL,7,FHis family said that in September
OL,8,F2024, the University told him that he
OL,9,Fhad not been awarded a grade for one
OL,10,Fcourse and would therefore not be
OL,11,Feligible to graduate with an Honours
OL,12,Fdegree.
OL,14,FHis mother posthumously collected his
OL,15,Fdegree in December after an internal
OL,16,Finvestigation found that her son had
OL,17,Fbeen awarded the wrong grade and
OL,18,Fshould have graduated with a 2:1
OL,19,FHonours degree.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
