OL,3,CGlasgow University accused of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' in report into
OL,5,Cstudent's death
OL,7,FA Quality Assurance Agency (QAA)
OL,8,Freport found systemic risks around the
OL,9,Facademic processes and student
OL,10,Fexperiences following Brown's case.
OL,12,FThe review found that the mistake was
OL,13,Fnot spotted by university staff -
OL,14,Finstead, it was picked up by two
OL,15,Finternal exam boards, or an external
OL,16,Fexam board.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
