OL,7,FIn response to the report, Ms Scott
OL,8,Fsaid that findings supported the
OL,9,F"family's concerns at the level of
OL,10,Fincompetence within the University of
OL,11,FGlasgow, which they feel places
OL,12,Fstudents at serious risk".
OL,14,FThe lawyer for the family and former
OL,15,Frector at the University, Aamer Anwar,
OL,16,Fsaid: "This investigation, triggered
OL,17,Fby Ethan's death, is a damning
OL,18,Findictment of systemic failures at the
OL,19,FUniversity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
