OL,3,CGlasgow University accused of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' in report into
OL,5,Cstudent's death
OL,7,F"Ethan's family are sickened by the
OL,8,Fgaslighting they endured as the
OL,9,FUniversity claimed publicly there were
OL,10,Fno systemic failures, in fact this
OL,11,Freport shows their internal report
OL,12,Fsaid the opposite - there were several
OL,13,Fother instances at the Geography
OL,14,Fschool, and they also failed to carry
OL,15,Fout any investigations into 23 other
OL,16,Fschools.
OL,18,F"The University's actions to date are
OL,19,Fshameful, and it is time that they
OL,20,Ffully declared how many other students
OL,21,Fhave suffered in this way.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
