OL,7,F"Ethan's family are devastated, but
OL,8,Fthey want a legacy of change and no
OL,9,Ffurther manipulation of the facts."
OL,11,FThe review looked into how grades are
OL,12,Fawarded, extension requests and
OL,13,Funiversity communication with
OL,14,Fstudents, among other lines of enquiry.
OL,16,FInvestigators found a number of areas
OL,17,Fin need of improvement and issued a
OL,18,Fsummary list of 21 specific
OL,19,Frecommendations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
