OL,3,CGlasgow University accused of
OL,4,C'systemic failures' in report into
OL,5,Cstudent's death
OL,7,FAmong the recommendations, the report
OL,8,Fcalled for extra "liaison meetings"
OL,9,Fover the next two years to keep track
OL,10,Fof progress. The University's next
OL,11,Fmajor external peer review would also
OL,12,Fbe brought forward by a year to 2027-
OL,13,F28 to check progress against the
OL,14,Frecommendations in the report.
OL,16,FGlasgow University will now have to
OL,17,Fsubmit an action plan within four
OL,18,Fweeks, showcasing how it will address
OL,19,Fthe weaknesses found in the report.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
