OL,7,FReflecting on the findings of the
OL,8,Freview, the family has said they feel
OL,9,FGlasgow University was attempting to
OL,10,Fmislead the public and further
OL,11,Fminimise the serious concerns
OL,12,Fidentified by the Scottish Funding
OL,13,FCouncil's initial investigation.
OL,15,FIn a statement issued by family
OL,16,Flawyers, they said: "The family hold
OL,17,Fthe University of Glasgow responsible
OL,18,Ffor Ethan's s death due to their
OL,19,Fmultiple levels of incompetence. Ethan
OL,20,Fasked for help from the University of
OL,21,FGlasgow, and none came.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
