OL,7,FA University spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Fare profoundly sorry that Ethan
OL,9,Ftragically took his own life and
OL,10,Funderstand the deep distress it has
OL,11,Fcaused his family. We offer a sincere
OL,12,Fapology as well as our deepest
OL,13,Fsympathy.
OL,15,F"Following an internal investigation
OL,16,Finto assessment regulations, the
OL,17,FUniversity self-referred to the
OL,18,FScottish Funding Council.
